Package: breedeng
Title: Breeding Analytics Engine
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Taylor", "Anderson", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "tayloranthonyanderson@gmail.com")
Description: Pluggable mixed-model engine for plant breeding trial analysis:
    BLUPs/BLUEs, heritability, and selection indices, with deterministic
    tool-safe operations that power an embedded AI assistant. Backends are
    swappable behind one contract (lme4, rrBLUP today; BLUPF90/GCTA later).
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    lme4,
    rrBLUP,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
